Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.61,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:06.60,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,some bothersome demons \Nappeared in the Fanta-C World,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:11.28,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,so Tombo-E Girl was summoned and the demons \Nwere sealed inside Fan-C Cards. The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.25,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,Or so the legend says, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:17.53,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,But one day the princess, who had \Ncompletely forgotten the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.52,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,dropped the Fan-C Cards into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:23.29,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,a fountain connected to Earth, \Ncausing a disaster, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:28.66,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,Since evil demons are so tough, \Ntheir magic remains in the Fan-C Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:31.31,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,and anything they touch \Nturns into a monster, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.85,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,Because these troublesome \Nmonsters need to be dealt with,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:38.44,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,I had Komugi-chan become Tombo-E Girl, pyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:41.43,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,But she's working so slowly, \Nwe've hardly gathered any at all, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.68,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll suck you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.28,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,By the time she gathers all 108 Fan-C Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:55.28,Main - Italics,USAP,0,0,0,,she won't be Tombo-E Girl, \Nshe'll be Tombo-E Grandma, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.03,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,No!
