Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.29,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,Large numbers of traffic \Nsafety mascot Pipopapo-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.34,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,have appeared across the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.50,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,surprising passers-by—
