Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.75,quiz show,,0,0,0,,Why is there \None open seat \Non a full train?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.75,quiz show,,0,0,0,,{\an2}Today's \Nguest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.75,quiz show,,0,0,0,,{\an2}Saionji\NKokona-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.53,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,The question is, "Why is there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.70,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,one open seat on a full train?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.51,Main - Top - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I believe there's someone sitting \Nthere that I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.02,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I was sure I left my bra here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.26,Main - Top - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,Ah, like a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.60,Main - Top - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.19,Main - Top - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There could be a spirit sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.77,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I could've given a better answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This one's for Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:56.98,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.24,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'll upload it to my blog later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:04.50,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.70,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.04,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.72,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm still half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.88,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Yes, off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.47,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Work hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.28,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.60,poster text,,0,0,0,,Let's All Take a\NBicycle Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:30.89,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:42.53,Ep Title,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,Stalker?! \NKokona-chan's Close Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.73,Main,TEACHER,0,0,0,,On to question three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.53,Main,TEACHER,0,0,0,,Saionji-san, could you translate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.44,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.46,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,"Nancy realized that the CD she had lent to Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.38,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,three months ago wasn't going to be returned."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I hate marathons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan, let's run together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.71,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.00,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Yo, yo, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.77,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Anyone who suggests that \Nis gonna betray you, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.47,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.90,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,I just heard a noise from in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.82,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.67,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Perhaps there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.81,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,a pervert hiding in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.07,Main,BOTH,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.97,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Given that there are idols in our class,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.73,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,I'd say we're a likely target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.33,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,Hey, pervert, what'chu up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.91,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.65,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.42,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I-I'm not afraid of a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Come on out, perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was just our imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.17,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.17,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,I definitely heard something, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.93,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Yeah, me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Come on. PE is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.32,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.33,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Recently I learned how to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.78,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,tie cherry stems in knots with my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.53,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Okay, let's see you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.53,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.41,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.37,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.04,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,That was brilliant, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.36,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You can make a living doing tricks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.54,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I was impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.05,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.85,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.55,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Rakugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.10,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I've been getting more variety show \Nappearances lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.18,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.71,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.76,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,but why not relax while you're in transit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.34,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You need to rest sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.78,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Just look at Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.81,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,It's important to be that relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.20,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:45.48,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Watching Komugi-chan gives me energy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.66,window text,,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.66,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.65,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Excuse us, President Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:50.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.27,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.49,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.66,Main,AI,0,0,0,,How's work been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.51,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Very fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:58.42,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.91,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Is there something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:03.64,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.01,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.11,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Don't worry about troubling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.54,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.14,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.22,Main,AI,0,0,0,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.88,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Considering it could be a stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:21.28,Main,AI,0,0,0,,I'll have security increased around \Nyour school and dorm, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.41,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Sorry for causing so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.23,Main,AI,0,0,0,,It's no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.74,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Once something happens, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:31.29,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Your parents are letting us look \Nafter their beloved daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.53,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Say something sooner next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.62,dorm mimosa - night,SIGN,0,0,0,,Nijigaoka Academy Dorm Mimosa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.62,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,I got a call from the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.41,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,I'm keeping watch over this \Ndorm, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.42,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,I won't let a single pest in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.12,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.42,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,There's a yuzu bath in the \Ncommunal bathroom tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.28,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Go take a dip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.93,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.52,Main - Flashback,MOM,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan, you place first in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.53,Main - Flashback,MOM,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.72,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,It's great that you work so hard at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.60,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,Your mom and dad are so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.79,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,You don't have to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.73,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,There are plenty of other ways \Nto nurture your talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.29,Main - Flashback,MOM,0,0,0,,Tokyo is far away, and you've got school, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.40,Main - Flashback,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I can make it on my own. \NI'll study hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.65,Main - Flashback,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I want to become an idol, whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.84,Main - Flashback,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.41,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,Be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.91,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it, \Nyou have to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.81,Main - Flashback,MOM,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.55,Main - Flashback,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.03,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I have to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.17,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I have a traffic safety event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.77,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I need to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.07,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,The Traffic Safety Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.28,Main - Italics,TV,0,0,0,,Our special guest is the \Npopular idol Mitaka Ai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.32,safety fest,,0,0,0,,{banner text}Traffic Safety Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.19,Main - Italics,AI,0,0,0,,I'm Mitaka Ai, 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.30,Main - Italics,AI,0,0,0,,My favorite traffic safety sign is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.46,Main - Italics,AI,0,0,0,,"indicated direction only."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.79,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The president is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I have to work harder. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:24.14,yellow text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,1)}Traffic Safety Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.14,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.65,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.41,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.83,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Where's your favorite idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.78,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Over there? Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.78,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.42,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Bathed in the summer sun's rays
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:51.97,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,When we're worn out from playing, \Nwe'll say goodnight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:07.60,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,There's a feeling in my \Nheart that I want to convey
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:13.49,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Within our clasped hands is a warm light
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:18.21,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,If you count all the dreams you've embraced
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:22.20,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,And play the song of the twinkling stars
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:28.28,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,All your worries will disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.88,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,As long as we're together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:37.72,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,We can relax and be ourselves anytime,\Nlike singing, dancing birds
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:43.18,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Even when you're feeling down, \Nyou'll feel better right away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:49.56,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Bathed in the hot summer sun's rays, \Nwe play in the water like children
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.98,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Then wipe ourselves dry with \Ntowels and say goodnight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:10:00.82,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Believing that we'll be smiling \Ntogether again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.47,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.72,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Onstage is the idol who just performed \Nthat lovely song for us, Saionji Kokona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.43,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Joining her are Kisaragi Tsukasa-san \Nand Tachibana Yuto-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.73,Main,MC,0,0,0,,who appear on the traffic \Nsafety posters with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.48,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Also with us is traffic \Nsafety mascot Pipopapo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.19,safety short,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(486,1)}Traffic Safety Short
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.19,safety short - red,TEXT,0,0,0,,Cycling Love
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.55,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I thought our happiness would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.51,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.14,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Why were we riding double on that bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.46,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,while listening to music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:56.21,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,If only I'd taken a bicycle class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.40,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.54,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.72,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Signing up is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.96,Main,BOTH,0,0,0,,Let's all take a bicycle class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.27,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.91,Main,MC,0,0,0,,How was that, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.50,Main,MC,0,0,0,,What was it like performing in that short?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.69,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Well, it's a very sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan is amazing. She can do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.55,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It made me realize the \Nimportance of traffic safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.24,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,She's such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.25,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah. I totally respect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.96,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,You work hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.66,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,You've been fickle since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:36.25,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,You've never managed to stick with anything,\Nexcept being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Well, it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.63,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan invited me to join her when
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.66,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I still only dreamed of becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.40,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That's why I work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.81,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Can't you put that effort \Ntowards your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.49,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.07,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-san, Kokona-san, thank you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.20,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Good work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.40,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.16,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.09,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.47,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.20,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.44,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.93,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What the heck happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.80,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.40,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.90,green room,SIGN,0,0,0,,Green Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.90,green room - name,SIGN,0,0,0,,Saionji \NKokona-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.33,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Kokona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.31,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.63,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You're on in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.39,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Excuse me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.34,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Ponpokopon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.59,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.31,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,My name is Tanu-P, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.45,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I-It's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.86,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Sorry for scaring you, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:29.24,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Due to the circumstances, I've been \Nwatching you for a long time, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.77,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You're the one who's been watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.83,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Indeed, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.13,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.33,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Based on my observations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.01,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I've concluded that you're perfect, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:45.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.79,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Not only are you pure, \Nrighteous, and beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.90,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,but you're also intelligent, \Nearnest, hardworking, ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.95,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,you have a lovely navel, and \Nyou always try your hardest, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:59.37,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,You're also kind, showing concern \Ntoward animals and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:03.23,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,You're considerate of those around you,\Nyou have a lovely navel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.67,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,you're responsible, perfect, and impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:09.58,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,In other words, you are none \Nother than perfeccable, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.55,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, it's an octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Put glasses on him, and he's a serious octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.26,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There's a monster nearby, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.59,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's time to Chan-G, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.25,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? Can't I eat lunch first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.76,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Do you want to become one \Nof those Cs you hate, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Don't talk about Cs while I'm eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.70,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I would like you to become \Na girl whose legend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.22,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,has been passed down for \Ngenerations in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:40.18,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I'd like you to become a Tombo-E Girl, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:40.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.48,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.71,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what's going on, \Nbut you seem to be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.16,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.30,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.70,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster nearby, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.53,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Would you be willing to Chan-G immediately, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.87,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.48,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Marisol miral sparklism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:59.10,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Flaming miral penifore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.06,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:05.38,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I've never felt anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.86,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop, cop, cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.88,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I'll arrest you, cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.14,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop, cop, cop, cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.16,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:13.85,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.14,under cop car,,0,0,0,,Traffic Safety Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.35,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The Magical Nurse has arrived full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.78,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,This is bad, pyon! We're doomed, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.89,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.99,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Who goes there, cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:31.99,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,All evildoers who disrupt order, \Neven my master, must be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The Magical Maid has arrived with grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.44,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,What's this? She seems to have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.83,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,changed Tombo-E Girl's name, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.22,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,A new Tombo-E Girl has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.80,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Now watch how she ChanG-ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:53.33,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Chanting it deciphers the code\Nprogrammed into the incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.27,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Marisol miral sparklism!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.59,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Flaming miral penifore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.22,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It scans Kokona's entire body while
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.58,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,simultaneously sending the \Ndata to the Fanta-C World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.56,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's instantly analyzed, and \NChan-G rays are fired at Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.56,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The rays turn Kokona's dutiful heart into
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.97,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Amazoni-N Cells, activating \Ntheir maximum Tombo-E potential
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.47,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and reconstructing her body and costume,\Ncompleting the Chan-G.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.86,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,On average, the transformation \Ntakes 0.02 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.94,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She's finally appeared, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,All right! An ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.41,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She's our enemy, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? No way. She looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.46,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You're awfully easygoing, to make \Nyour appearance now, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.26,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I've already collected this many, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.30,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I simply thought it'd be more fair
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.59,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,to give a lesser animal like you a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.68,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I did it out of pity, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.27,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,What did you say, pyon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.85,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Stop ignoring me, cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.62,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Arrest them, cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Violence is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.82,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.82,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Maid-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:54.20,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.08,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,What's this, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.21,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's time for your punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.96,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Magical Whip of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.72,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Grovel before me, servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.33,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Ecstasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:21.14,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I feel as though your \Npersonality has changed, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.57,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.23,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It doesn't work that way, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:28.80,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Kneel before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:29.73,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I shall take good care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.11,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I like that sound you're making!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,She's kind of... incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.12,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Pyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:43.75,Main,TAMUP,0,0,0,,P-Perhaps you should finish him off with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.62,Main,TAMUP,0,0,0,,your Icky Icky Aja-PA Beam now, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You weren't all that tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.21,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop, cop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.25,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The Icky Icky Aja-PA Beam is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.11,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,a blast of hot air produced by the intermingling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:07.87,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,of the heat released during \Nthe sharp rise in temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:11.12,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,of the Amazoni-N Cells and Kokona's soft skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.68,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's a special attack that purifies enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.37,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See you later, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:22.86,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Maid Burning Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.75,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:36.84,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Keep a safe distance between your \Nlife and the car in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.02,police car monster,TEXT,0,0,0,,Police Car \NMonster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:48.02,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This Fan-C Card is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.77,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,They came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.45,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Pyon! We must steal the \NFan-C Card from her, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But she already defeated \Nthe monster. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.84,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.61,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,How barbaric, to want to steal something, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.62,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I've got just the spell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Magical Sticky Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What is this? It's all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.77,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Have fun playing with my slime, \Nyou bone-headed nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:18.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.21,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.12,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Damn it! Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.73,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,What's wrong, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.71,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Where's the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.67,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,What's this? You defeated it for me, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.99,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.09,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.49,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm just glad the problem was solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.88,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I feel refreshed, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.42,Main,MC,0,0,0,,It's time to wrap things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.51,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.51,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:01.47,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.64,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:08.40,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Let's have a big round of \Napplause for our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.53,window text,,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.53,Main,AI,0,0,0,,The event went well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.59,Main,AI,0,0,0,,and the stalker case was resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.93,Main,AI,0,0,0,,That settles things for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:50.58,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.79,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What? I thought you'd already heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.54,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Your dorm mother caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:00.71,Main,AI,0,0,0,,He was sneaking around in the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,So there really was a stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.66,Main,AI,0,0,0,,From now on, if anything happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.55,Main,AI,0,0,0,,just tell me instead of \Ntrying to handle it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.30,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Whether it's a concern or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:12.77,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Anyway, President Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:18.85,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:23.10,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Someday I hope to become a super idol like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:25.86,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,so I plan to work even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Poko, poko, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:44.80,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:36.61,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Kokona here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.75,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That stalker business really shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:39.54,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Stalking and streaking sound \Nsimilar but are totally different,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.80,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,so be careful when you're doing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.99,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The next episode is \N"The Magical Sister Arrives!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:50.00,next ep title,TEXT,0,0,0,,The Magical Sister Arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.39,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,See you again soon, Master.